    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Up for sale is a dependable vehicle in good overall condition, perfect for anyone seeking a reliable daily driver. The engine starts up without hesitation and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides consistent shifting through all gears. The exterior is well-maintained, showing only minor cosmetic wear consistent with careful use, such as a few small stone chips. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all major features and electronics functioning as intended. This car has been regularly serviced and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
