      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to offer this exemplary vehicle, presented in absolute showroom condition. Meticulously preserved and showing no signs of wear, this specimen serves as a benchmark for the model. The exterior retains its original luster, while the interior remains in a state of flawless refinement. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade vehicle that has been maintained to the highest possible standards of automotive excellence. Discerning buyers will appreciate the unparalleled integrity and mechanical superiority of this pristine offering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
